props.synopsis: An Australian pilot along with two Papua New Guinean technicians has been freed after they were kidnapped "at gunpoint" from a remote telecommunications site in PNG's highlands

image.altText: An aerial shot of a dry brown river in Greenough, the Midwest. There's a tiny green car at the mouth.

image.altText: university cap graduation generic

image.altText: People holding up signs in a protest

image.altText: Black and white photo of young girl with stern expression holding one hand in her other, with parents smiling either side.

image.altText: A side-on photo of a man wearing a blue suit, white shirt and yellow tie gesturing with his right hand while speaking on stage.

image.altText: Gail Kelsey smiling with a broad brimmed hat on.

image.altText: A man in scrubs stands in a medical room.

image.altText: A woman in a blazer looking stern.

title.children: Complainant in Bruce Lehrmann alleged rape case to be cross-examined in Toowoomba
